h1. uploadForm

h2. Purpose

Creates a form that can submit multi-part data for file uploads.

h2. Examples

{code:xml}
<g:uploadForm name="myUpload">
    <input type="file" name="myFile" />
</g:uploadForm>
{code}

h2. Description

Identical to the standard [form|tags] tag except that it sets the @enctype@ attribute to @"multipart/form-data"@ automatically.

Attributes

* @action@ (optional) - the name of the action to use in the link; if not specified the default action will be linked
* @controller@ (optional) - the name of the controller to use in the link; if not specified the current controller will be linked
* @id@ (optional) - The id to use in the link
* @url@ (optional) - A map containing the action, controller, id etc.

